						<li><a href="#">고객센터(평일/주말 09:00~18:00): 1234-1234(유료)</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;|&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>
						<li><a href="#">호스팅제공자: (주)티켓루팡</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;|&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>
						<li><a href="#">&copy;TicketLupin Corp. All rights reserved.</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</li><br>
					</ul>
				</span>
			</div>
		</footer>
